  "description": [
    "Friday 12 October 1962 Navy Museum To Serve As A Memorial Navvmen the world over are being given an opportunity to contribute to the establishment of a naval museum adjacent to his toric Independence Hall in Phil adelphia Pemberton House the naval museum will serve as a memorial to the Navy ami its significant role in America s history In an era troubled by false ideologies Secretary of the Navy Fred Forth noted in announcing the project we need to arm our selves with clear understanding of the true historical record of America and the role which we in the naval service have inherited For that reason he continued the establishment of a naval mu seum adjacent to historic Inde pendence Hall as a memorial to the Navy and those serving the country in it is brought to the attention of the Naval Establish ment so that all hands may have an opportunity to contribute to this commendable project Contributions should be sent to Pemberton House Naval Museum Committee Navy League of the VS Independence National His torical Park Philadelphia Pa Service Station Offers Free Seat Belt Installation A safety device which has proved its value in helping curb auto"
